  "chunks": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "Half the community swapped MCP for Skills.",
      "checksum": "sha256:db43bf265b75e415182680562495169b1d4ab8a82a57ff0b94949bf3ea4ce10b",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 2.647074829931973,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "Here's when to pick each. MCP is the Model Context Protocol.",
      "checksum": "sha256:cfc6a89d79d172c20e9ea8579dd6a1d65d5e23f73c118b4cba3230a4f1065faa",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 3.7151927437641725,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 7
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "An open standard for connecting Claude Code to external tools and data.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1d53d8703912ea10c05163b02880e74afcc11af7178c5ccbc80d50dd578bd24b",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 4.133151927437642,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 18
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "Hundreds of servers exist. GitHub, Sentry, Postgres, Slack, Jira, Figma, and more.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2ef0c28009e5072ba8c7a6a8548bab3752ba5e9fcb53ca3f82aa69ea76c39b96",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 5.294149659863946,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 30
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "Installation is one command. Type claude mcp add and the server name plus URL.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d0beb33cf95435068b0d1aab1e591039f14ec91f709dbde29f0e4d5a95d0db5e",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 4.829750566893424,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 42
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "Three transports are supported. HTTP for remote servers.",
      "checksum": "sha256:810876b1a3d2a9572d9ed64c68316f964a8de3b4e3ed1c2faf506f74bc1aa2df",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 3.575873015873016,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 56
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "SSE for legacy. Standard input output for local processes.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0d81564e24d1e9ebda4c1229b5536843f41ae056d5a44e000d6a46397486907a",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 3.436553287981859,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 64
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "Context cost can balloon when you connect many servers.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6ec9bec97453ca86e349cff849b0eac90cd64c48d9c985a380d2714373faceb2",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 2.972154195011338,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 73
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "Tool Search dynamically loads tools on demand to mitigate it.",
      "checksum": "sha256:85903d3e785b7cb0a6b99f9c99397fb19c7a31fead0b7705f055d82f992092a4",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 3.2043537414965986,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 82
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "Five decision examples. External SaaS API like GitHub?",
      "checksum": "sha256:a5b29f43cc3456eadd665361a68fed919ace2c63ed3497a1dec0a3b40d1adf62",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 3.2043537414965986,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 92
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "MCP. Custom team workflow? Skill. Database queries?",
      "checksum": "sha256:67c1d62b3bbcfd555864f4e0203c34c430861b1042f769289b3fd36ae563ff60",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 3.4829931972789114,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 100
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "MCP. Coding standards check? Skill. Third-party data fetch?",
      "checksum": "sha256:d5daeedba7f64718584790749df9829af7b003f4c06f0fbbc0e7fb8acb637bbe",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 3.9938321995464854,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 107
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "MCP. The rule. External tools and data go through MCP.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2d094687d268697b48c624bc08cdfdfd930e71b1d22d592b257d112549ca9ce2",
      "wav": "chunk-12.wav",
      "duration": 3.8545124716553287,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 115
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "text": "Custom procedures and team standards become Skills.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9cbd2558d94901023ac3863adc18cfd7c306443e26f29fed64671c02df01cef1",
      "wav": "chunk-13.wav",
      "duration": 2.8792743764172335,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 125
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "text": "Watch the 13 minute deep dive for the full Claude Code customization system.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6e5ddf6258f4ec8c2579a226824dc5b2ab5e830c5bd5a3db8fd8ae6111fbc7a6",
      "wav": "chunk-14.wav",
      "duration": 4.133151927437642,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 132
    }
  ]
